### List users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users

### Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?q=alice

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/1

### Update user
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{"accountStatus": "Overdue", "name": "Carson Jones"}

### Add subscription
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/1/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{"licensePlate": "NEW-999", "type": "Pro"}

### Transfer subscription (change license plate)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1/subscriptions/s1
Content-Type: application/json

{"licensePlate": "TRF-001"}

### Change subscription type
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1/subscriptions/s1
Content-Type: application/json

{"type": "Deluxe"}

### Cancel subscription
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1/subscriptions/s1
Content-Type: application/json

{"status": "Cancelled"}